description: Erection of four residential blocks (2 x 5 Storey and 2 x 4 storey) to provide 78 residential units comprising 22 one bed, 35 two bed,  16 three bed and 5 four bed flats; erection of a five storey plus basement warehouse building comprising 3,667 sq.m of B8 floorspace plus 36 basement and 8 ground level car parking spaces (44 spaces); demolition of existing warehouse buildings.
